{"id": "ChIJbxqeVHPDwoAR6SBBOUZdLBc", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 1701, "displayName": {"text": "CAVA", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Mediterranean restaurant for thoughtful food with customizable greens & grains bowls, pitas & salad.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJbxqeVHPDwoAR6SBBOUZdLBc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tveVVFWm1UV0V6VlRsdlkyZzFiWGhRWms1eWFVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Keanu provided excellent customer service at Kava. When I got to the register to pay, he was incredibly friendly, professional, and attentive. He had such a positive attitude and made the interaction feel genuine and welcoming. Even while things were busy, he stayed patient, efficient, and kind. Honestly, everyone up to him was amazing, but Keanu especially stood out because of how personable and professional he was. Kava is lucky to have a team like that!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Keanu provided excellent customer service at Kava. When I got to the register to pay, he was incredibly friendly, professional, and attentive. He had such a positive attitude and made the interaction feel genuine and welcoming. Even while things were busy, he stayed patient, efficient, and kind. Honestly, everyone up to him was amazing, but Keanu especially stood out because of how personable and professional he was. Kava is lucky to have a team like that!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mari Bacos", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115057306277924392004/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVS5Wwam6aj6w5UBRamk2tS2E_PnyMNDtg_FBxnaEY1-Ta6PNRxvw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-11T20:17:54.621590781Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tveVVFWm1UV0V6VlRsdlkyZzFiWGhRWms1eWFVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tveVVFWm1UV0V6VlRsdlkyZzFiWGhRWms1eWFVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c373549e1a6f:0x172c5d46394120e9"}, {"name": "places/ChIJbxqeVHPDwoAR6SBBOUZdLBc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sbVpubGxhMncyY21oeVV6UjBaVFF6VUZOaFdWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "The food is definitely high-quality and the ingredients are fresh, which I appreciated. Unfortunately, the actual taste didn’t fit my palate. The taste of the combination of sauces and ingredients didn’t seem to blend well together…😮‍💨\nBesides, it’ll be much more quicker if you order online first.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The food is definitely high-quality and the ingredients are fresh, which I appreciated. Unfortunately, the actual taste didn’t fit my palate. The taste of the combination of sauces and ingredients didn’t seem to blend well together…😮‍💨\nBesides, it’ll be much more quicker if you order online first.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "JASMINE LIN", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112661560453976897213/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9gpXD1wVGtiZ3tVX2u5SfLsCHSZRS-GSoQqLyrepfQsaLd1m-=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-30T14:23:29.593275973Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sbVpubGxhMncyY21oeVV6UjBaVFF6VUZOaFdWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sbVpubGxhMncyY21oeVV6UjBaVFF6VUZOaFdWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c373549e1a6f:0x172c5d46394120e9"}, {"name": "places/ChIJbxqeVHPDwoAR6SBBOUZdLBc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNdGRHVnpUVEoyZERSMloyWTFkbXhITm1jM1psRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Whoever made this cava bowl on Thursday Apr 30 at 6:29 pm for door dash should be fired. This is the 4th or 5th time at this specific location where we door dashed a similar bowl and it was made with such little love, interest or even guidance of the order. This chef should be fired. Do. It go here. I think they do it on purpose because for DoorDash there is nothing you can do but get a refund. We ordered chicken and got steak, the lettuce was sad, the bowl looked pathetic. We spent $23 on a 1/4 bag of lettuce - this is a joke. Avoid avoid avoid.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Whoever made this cava bowl on Thursday Apr 30 at 6:29 pm for door dash should be fired. This is the 4th or 5th time at this specific location where we door dashed a similar bowl and it was made with such little love, interest or even guidance of the order. This chef should be fired. Do. It go here. I think they do it on purpose because for DoorDash there is nothing you can do but get a refund. We ordered chicken and got steak, the lettuce was sad, the bowl looked pathetic. We spent $23 on a 1/4 bag of lettuce - this is a joke. Avoid avoid avoid.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "CSH", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104654673646433095881/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcOSqu4GmKwEtNSz_YP8mJIuPu0qdHTZtpk2sXjC3CljxMyZE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-01T02:19:21.338393595Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNdGRHVnpUVEoyZERSMloyWTFkbXhITm1jM1psRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNdGRHVnpUVEoyZERSMloyWTFkbXhITm1jM1psRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c373549e1a6f:0x172c5d46394120e9"}, {"name": "places/ChIJbxqeVHPDwoAR6SBBOUZdLBc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205ak5HdDRMV2RpTTFwSGVHNWFkbkIyV21kNk5IYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I had an amazing experience at CAVA! The food was fresh, flavorful, and prepared perfectly. What really made my visit stand out was the outstanding customer service from Ana and Faith. They were both incredibly friendly, welcoming, and patient while helping me with my order. Their positive attitudes and attention to detail made the whole experience even better.\n\nIt’s clear that Ana and Faith genuinely care about their customers and take pride in their work. Great food and even better service, I will definitely be coming back. Thank you both for making my visit so enjoyable!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I had an amazing experience at CAVA! The food was fresh, flavorful, and prepared perfectly. What really made my visit stand out was the outstanding customer service from Ana and Faith. They were both incredibly friendly, welcoming, and patient while helping me with my order. Their positive attitudes and attention to detail made the whole experience even better.\n\nIt’s clear that Ana and Faith genuinely care about their customers and take pride in their work. Great food and even better service, I will definitely be coming back. Thank you both for making my visit so enjoyable!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kyle Jericho", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115308565548049336740/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZVIKX9BnxiqzSCrCFeWDyzacXiaJdLqhrAqVzfc4de8HBkjA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-02T04:21:28.724518745Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205ak5HdDRMV2RpTTFwSGVHNWFkbkIyV21kNk5IYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205ak5HdDRMV2RpTTFwSGVHNWFkbkIyV21kNk5IYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c373549e1a6f:0x172c5d46394120e9"}, {"name": "places/ChIJbxqeVHPDwoAR6SBBOUZdLBc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjl